## Next Steps

1.  Synchronize and complete the JSON schemas in `draft-ietf-rpp-json` to match updates in `draft-ietf-rpp-data-objects`.
2.  Refine the value-based matching algorithm in the JSON draft and gather implementation feedback.
3.  Reorganize IANA registry definitions in the data objects draft to make them manageable for IANA.